These are the scripts for Block Breaker game
Ball.cs contains all the logic for the ball to function including launching, clamping velocity and slowing down time
BreakableBlocks.cs contains all the logic for the breakable blocks including health and damage system, increasing special meter, etc.
UnbreakableBlocks.cs contains all the logic for the Unbreakable blocks.
Paddle.cs contains all the logic for the player and the paddle including launching ball, shooting laser, setting paddle position through mouse etc.
